title: Cowboys, Running Backs, Browns, Aaron Rodgers, & athletes-actors
itunes:title: Cowboys, Running Backs, Browns, Aaron Rodgers, & athletes-actors
description:
Colin discusses the Dallas Cowboys offensive line, running backs, and what he would do with Ezekiel Elliott. Also his thoughts on the Cleveland Browns upcoming season, Aaron Rodgers friction with coaches, and which athletes remind him of certain actors. Guests include Hue Jackson, Will Blackmon, Peter King, Josh Norman, and Jason McIntyre.
